        public android.graphics.RectF computeBounds()
        Compute the bounds of the control points of the path, and write the answer into bounds. If the path contains 0 or 1 points, the bounds is set to (0,0,0,0). 计算笔迹的控制点的边界，把结果写入到返回值。如果只有0或者1个点，边界会被设置为(0,0,0,0)
